text: Mathias Logelin (24 April 1907 - 31 October 1999) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1928 Summer Olympics and the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1999 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:People from Differdange
